review_blob: Considering that it has bud light in its name I was already expecting little from this beer. All in all though it is not that bad, its smells like a metal refinery worker might smell after a long days work and tastes like the rape child of a pyramid hefeweizen and bud light.
I had better expectations for this beer but was let down. Has a smooth aftertaste and pours nicely. Leaves very good lace in your glass.
